---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/contact.css';
---

<Layout title="Contactos - Pecaditos">
	<!-- Contact Hero -->
	<section class="contact-hero bg-cover bg-center py-20 text-center text-chocolate-dark" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg');">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1 class="hero-title text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Vamos falar de doces!</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle text-xl mb-8 animate-fadeIn">Contacta-nos para qualquer questão ou para contratares os nossos serviços</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Contact Ways -->
	<section class="contact-ways">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<h2 class="section-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Como nos podes contactar</h2>
			<div class="ways-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				<div class="way-card shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="way-icon text-3xl">📧</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Email</h3>
					<p>Envia-nos um email com as tuas questões ou pedidos de orçamento.</p>
					<a href="mailto:pecaditos1808@gmail.com" class="way-link text-blue-500">pecaditos1808@gmail.com</a>
				</div>
				<div class="way-card shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="way-icon text-3xl">📱</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Telefone</h3>
					<p>Liga-nos diretamente para conversarmos sobre os teus doces favoritos.</p>
					<div class="phone-numbers">
						<a href="tel:+351927169060" class="way-link text-blue-500">927 169 060</a>
						<a href="tel:+351937509957" class="way-link text-blue-500">937 509 957</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="way-card shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="way-icon text-3xl">📸</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Instagram</h3>
					<p>Segue-nos para veres as nossas criações mais recentes e estares a par de todas as novidades.</p>
					<span class="way-link coming-soon text-gray-500">@pecaditos (em breve)</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Find Us -->
	<section class="find-us bg-cover bg-center py-16" style="background-image: url('/images/map-bg.jpg');">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<div class="find-us-content flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
				<div class="find-us-text md:w-1/2">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Onde nos encontrar</h2>
					<p class="mb-4">
						Estamos constantemente a percorrer as melhores feiras e eventos da região de Terras de Basto. Fica atento às nossas redes sociais para saberes sempre onde vamos estar!
					</p>
					<div class="location-highlight flex items-center">
						<span class="location-icon text-2xl mr-2">📍</span>
						<span>Terras de Basto</span>
					</div>

				</div>
				<div class="find-us-visual md:w-1/2 flex justify-center">
					<div class="map-illustration relative">
						<div class="map-icon text-4xl">🗺️</div>
						<div class="floating-pins absolute top-0 left-0">
							<span class="text-2xl">📌</span>
							<span class="text-2xl">📍</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Contact Form -->
	<section class="contact-form-section py-16">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<h2 class="section-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Envia-nos uma Mensagem</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle mb-8">
				Preenche o formulário e entraremos em contacto contigo o mais rapidamente possível. Queremos saber tudo sobre o teu evento ou as tuas preferências doces!
			</p>
			<form class="contact-form max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
				<div class="form-row grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nome *</label>
						<input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-chocolate-dark focus:border-chocolate-dark sm:text-sm">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Email *</label>
						<input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-chocolate-dark focus:border-chocolate-dark sm:text-sm">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-row grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Telefone</label>
						<input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-chocolate-dark focus:border-chocolate-dark sm:text-sm">
					</div>
					<div class="form-group">
						<label for="event-type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Tipo de Evento</label>
						<select id="event-type" name="event-type" class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-chocolate-dark focus:border-chocolate-dark sm:text-sm">
							<option value="">Seleciona uma opção</option>
							<option value="aniversario">Aniversário</option>
							<option value="casamento">Casamento</option>
							<option value="corporativo">Evento Corporativo</option>
							<option value="feira">Feira/Festival</option>
							<option value="outro">Outro</option>
						</select>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group mt-4">
					<label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Mensagem *</label>
					<textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Conta-nos mais sobre o teu evento ou o que procuras..." class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-chocolate-dark focus:border-chocolate-dark sm:text-sm"></textarea>
				</div>
				<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary form-submit mt-6 bg-chocolate-medium text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full shadow-md hover:bg-chocolate-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-chocolate-dark">
					<span class="btn-icon">📤</span>
					Enviar Mensagem
				</button>
			</form>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

